						<p>On a slab lying in a field to the west of the public well.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Tāraṇa, Māgha ba. 14, Tuesday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record the some grant to Kuṁṭhavaram Nārasiṁhaya by Immaḍi-Chikkarāya of Suguṭūru. In late characters.</p>						

